Node.Notes: Given that this is before the Fall and so there is only one recognized God, a reference to plural "gods" is unlikely. So, tree assumes "you will be like God, [you will be] those who know good and evil."
Uncertain. Could refer to God ("like God, [you will be] those who know good and evil") or gods ("like gods who know good and evil").
Uncertain whether a flame in the shape of a sword or a sword that throws off flames, though probably the latter.
